The_Geralt.title: The tale of the White Wolf
The_Geralt.author: Geralt of Rivia
The_Geralt.smallDes: The Witcher is a mutant in the mediveal time who also uses some demon arts tricks.
The_Geralt.thePara: The Witcher is a series of six fantasy novels and 15 short stories written by Polish author Andrzej Sapkowski. The series revolves around the eponymous witcher, Geralt of Rivia. In Sapkowski's works, witchers are beast hunters who develop supernatural abilities at a young age to battle wild beasts and monsters.

Sukuna.title: King of curses
Sukuna.author: Roymen Sukuna
Sukuna.smallDes: According to a legend, during the golden age of jujutsu over 1,000 years ago, Sukuna was an Imaginary Demon
Sukuna.thePara: Ryomen Sukuna (両りょう面めん宿すく儺な Ryomen Sukuna?), more often called just Sukuna (宿すく儺な Sukuna?), is a mighty cursed spirit known as the undisputed King of Curses (呪のろいの王おう Noroi no Ō?). He serves as one of the primary antagonists of the Jujutsu Kaisen series.
